{"about_the_game":"<strong>Welcome to House of Lies</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279610/extras/Main_Hall_Reveal_02.gif?t=1724312423\" /><br><br>In House of Lies, players take on the role of Ryan Evans, a struggling writer who takes a house-sitting job to finish his book. But what was meant to be a peaceful retreat quickly turns into a fight for survival when Ryan uncovers a twisted secret about the property he's caring for. It's up to Ryan to navigate through the terror-filled environments and solve intricate puzzles to uncover the truth.<br><br>In this first-person survival horror game, players will scavenge for resources, fight off enemies, and use their survival skills to survive the night. Can you unravel the mystery and escape the House of Lies?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279610/extras/Statue_Reveal.gif?t=1724312423\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279610/extras/Water_Puzzle.gif?t=1724312423\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1724312423","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279610/page.bg.jpg?t=1724312423","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279610/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1724312423","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279610/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1724312423","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"House of Lies features intense violence, blood, gore, and mature themes. Players will be required to shoot and kill zombies, as well as other human characters. The game also includes graphic depictio